#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:205
msgid ""
"Should *AvaTax* be needed for geo-localization, or with the *Amazon "
"Connector*, then install those modules individually by clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Install` on :guilabel:`Avatax for geo localization` "
"and :guilabel:`Amazon/Avatax Bridge`, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Jos *AvaTax*-moduulia tarvitaan geopaikallistamiseen tai *Amazon "
"Connectorin* kanssa, asenna kyseiset moduulit erikseen "
"napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Asenna` moduuleissa :guilabel:`Avatax for geo "
"localization` ja :guilabel:`Amazon/Avatax Bridge`."

