"In the **Expense** app, specify the invoicing policy for each expense "
"category. Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> "
"Expense Categories`. Click on the desired expense category or :doc:`create a "
"new one <expense_categories>`."
msgstr ""
