"Jokaisen maksutavan kohdalla on pakollista asettaa :guilabel:`SRI-maksutapa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:803
msgid ""
"Adding the :guilabel:`SRI Payment Method` is necessary to correctly generate "
