msgid ""
":doc:`Install </applications/general/apps_modules>` the :guilabel:`France - "
"Factur-X integration with Chorus Pro` (`l10n_fr_facturx_chorus_pro`) module."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Asenna </applications/general/apps_modules>` :guilabel:`Ranska - "
"Factur-X-integrointi Chorus Pron kanssa` (`l10n_fr_facturx_chorus_pro`) "
"-moduuli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:394
msgid ""
":ref:`Register <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol-registration>` with Peppol, as "
"invoices are sent from Odoo to Chorus Pro via the :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>` network."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Rekisteröidy <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol-registration>` Peppoliin, "
"koska laskut lähetetään Odoosta Chorus Proon :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>`-verkon kautta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:396
msgid ""
"If you don’t already have a Chorus Pro account, go to the `Chorus Pro "
"<https://portail.chorus-pro.gouv.fr/aife_csm>`_ page, click :guilabel:`Créer "
"un compte`, and create one."
msgstr ""
