msgid ""
"To automatically include a specific phrase in the XML and PDF of every "
"electronic invoice for a contact, select it in :guilabel:`Phrases` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Sales & purchase` tab of the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Jos haluat sisällyttää automaattisesti tietyn lauseen jokaisen yhteystahon "
"sähköisen laskun XML- ja PDF-tiedostoon, valitse se "
"yhteystietolomakkeen :guilabel:`Myynti ja ostot` "
"-välilehden :guilabel:`Lauseet` -kentästä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:202
msgid ""
"As part of the Guatemala localization module, taxes are automatically "
"created with their configuration and related financial accounts."
