msgid ":guilabel:`Validate` the delivery."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vahvista` toimitus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:307
msgid ":guilabel:`Confirm` the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vahvista` lasku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:308
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send`, and then enable :guilabel:`Send to eTIMS`."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Odeslat` a poté zapněte :guilabel:`Odeslat do eTIMS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:309
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send` to send the invoice."
msgstr "Klikněte na :guilabel:`Odeslat` pro odeslání faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:311
msgid ""
"Once the invoice has been sent and signed by the KRA, the following "
"information can be found on it:"
msgstr ""
"Kun KRA on lähettänyt ja allekirjoittanut laskun, siitä löytyvät seuraavat "
"tiedot:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:314
msgid "**KRA invoice number**;"
msgstr "**KRA-laskunumero**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:315
msgid ""
"Mandatory KRA invoice fields, such as **SCU information**, **date**, **SCU "
"ID**, **receipt number**, **item count**, **internal date**, and **receipt "
"signature**;"
msgstr ""
"Pakolliset KRA-laskulisäkentät, kuten **SCU-tiedot**, **päivämäärä**, **SCU-"
"tunnus**, **kuittinumero**, **tuotemäärä**, **sisäinen päivämäärä** ja "
"**kuitin allekirjoitus**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:317
msgid "The **KRA tax table**;"
msgstr "**KRA-verotaulukko**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:318
msgid "A unique **KRA QR code** for the signed invoice."
msgstr "Yksilöllinen **KRA QR-koodi** allekirjoitetulle laskulle."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:321
msgid "Imports"
msgstr "Tuonnit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:323
msgid ""
"Customs import codes are **automatically** fetched from the KRA eTIMS API "
"servers every day. To fetch them manually, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Tullituontikoodit **haetaan automaattisesti** KRA eTIMS API -palvelimilta "
"joka päivä. Hae ne manuaalisesti seuraavasti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:327
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Automation: Scheduled "
"Actions` and search for :guilabel:`KE eTIMS: Receive Customs Imports from "
"the OSCU`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Tekniset --> Automaatio: "
"Ajoitetut toiminnot` ja etsi :guilabel:`KE eTIMS: Receive Customs Imports "
"from the OSCU`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:331
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Customs Imports` to view "
"the imported codes."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Kirjanpito --> Toimittajat --> Tullituonnit` "
"tarkastellaksesi tuotuja koodeja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:333
msgid ""
"The following steps are required to send and have **customs imports** signed "
"by the KRA:"
msgstr ""
"Seuraavat vaiheet vaaditaan **tullituontien** lähettämiseen ja "
"allekirjoittamiseen KRA:ssa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:335
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Customs Imports`; The "
"customs import is fetched automatically from the KRA."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Kirjanpito --> Toimittajat --> Tullituonnit`. "
"Tullituonti haetaan automaattisesti KRA:sta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:337
msgid ""
"Match the imported item with an existing registered product in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` field (or create a product if no related product "
"exists)."
msgstr ""
"Yhdistä tuotu nimike olemassa olevaan rekisteröityyn "
"tuotteeseen :guilabel:`Tuote` -kentässä (tai luo tuote, jos vastaavaa "
"tuotetta ei ole)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:339
msgid "Set a vendor in the :guilabel:`Partner` field."
msgstr "Aseta toimittaja :guilabel:`Kumppani` -kenttään."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:340
msgid ""
"Based on the partner, match the imported item with its related purchase "
"order (see :ref:`purchase steps <kenya/purchases>`). The stock must be "
"correctly adjusted when the customs import is approved."
msgstr ""
"Yhdistä kumppanin perusteella tuotu nimike siihen liittyvään ostotilaukseen "
"(katso :ref:`oston vaiheet <kenya/purchases>`). Varasto on säädettävä "
"oikein, kun tullituonti hyväksytään."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:344
msgid ""
"If no related purchase order exists, create one and :guilabel:`Confirm` it. "
"Then, confirm the delivery by clicking :guilabel:`Receive Products`, "
"then :guilabel:`Validate` on the purchase order."
msgstr ""
