#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:966
msgid ":ref:`Automatic invoice <handling/legal>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Automaattinen lasku <handling/legal>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:967
msgid ""
":doc:`../../websites/ecommerce/products`: Set the :guilabel:`Invoicing "
"Policy` to :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` and define the "
