"setup>` :guilabel:`Contact`-lomakkeessa toimittajan laskua luotaessa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:364
msgid ""
"The |CIS| tax used in the vendor bill does not match the expected |CIS| "
"deduction rate for a :ref:`subcontractor <localization/united-kingdom/cis-"
